description: For All you girls out there.If you wanna find out if your boyfriend is gay, you must do what this girl did. I guess this chick had her suspicions about him. Either case, she was hanging out with her gay friends and they convinced her to call over her boyfriend to hang out. The plan was to, after he comes over, she was gonna leave for whatever excuse, and leave the boyfriend there, and the real gay guys were gonna try to find out if this dude was gay or not. Let me tell you guys something. Once the girl left, what the guys found out was something that I was not expecting AT ALL.
title: Pump It
